''', "function"

# A render-local declaration inside the body matters too — the outer auto-
# allocated index becomes a positional parameter of every nested factory,
# so a body-level `let i;` (from `i = ...`) would collide with it just like
# an inner explicit `for v, i in ...` would. The pre-scan now catches both.

