# ==============================================================================
# Boolean Prop Shorthand — JSX-style bare-identifier props
# ==============================================================================

# Bare identifier in a child-component arg list desugars to `name: true`.
# Matches JSX semantics: bare ident is ALWAYS a literal `true`, never a
# variable reference, even if a same-named local binding exists in scope.
# Scoped to PascalCase component calls inside `render` blocks; DOM elements
# and imperative calls outside `render` are unaffected.

